          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-white shadow-md p-6 border border-green-100">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-700">üåç Vision</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
            A future where nature and humanity thrive in harmony through
            collective environmental action.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->

    <% include ./partial/footer.ejs %>
  </body>
  <script src="/javascripts/aos.js"></script>
  <script>
    AOS.init({
      mirror: true,
    });
  </script>
